{"tid":1000903,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"求一個明珠台深夜播過嘅外國電影名","createTime":"2019-01-29T17:43:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T04:36:16.000Z","uid":234168,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5a935b3b1d99d5e73a2f17dd932964936b8b2d9e","tid":1000903,"uid":234168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:43:48.000Z","msg":"2006-2016年間，係明珠台深夜電影播過。<br />\n由於當時好眼瞓，淨係記得兩幕。<br />\n<br />\n1. 應該係男女主角，佢哋好似原本唔多啱瓦，但有次男嘅見到女嘅打劍(fencing)好勁，然後就好似俾個女嘅吸引咗啦。<br />\n2. 面具舞會入面，好似係有個好高名望嘅老人生日，來賓一pair pair咁向佢道賀，其中包括應該係男女主角。<br />\n<br />\n知道嘅人唔該幫吓我，呢個問題困擾咗我好耐，真係好想知電影名，等我可以睇番(我係睇戲一旦開始咗就要睇到結局嘅人)。<br />\n我唔係無試過自己搵答案，上埋wiki睇明珠台歷年播過嘅外購電影都無頭緒，簡直大海撈針，睇名根本唔會知內容係唔係我嗰套。<br />\nwiki: <a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/無綫電視外購美國電影列表\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%E7%84%A1%E7%B6%AB%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96%E5%A4%96%E8%B3%BC%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8&d=2pBoyAcJJfm%2FTk9I6oZxMD2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=e3d8d3c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/無綫電視外購美國電影列表</a>"},{"pid":"ad94829c8e4a357c6e1008d533894f421d93f1c5","tid":1000903,"uid":172608,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7bace38b17b2b9434c2514fe169543b32ba1d74e","tid":1000903,"uid":234168,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ad94829c8e4a357c6e1008d533894f421d93f1c5","tid":1000903,"uid":172608,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:46:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T17:56:47.000Z","msg":"唉&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a33b9a7e621d2b0b274c571d99308f22ce0d71b","tid":1000903,"uid":106950,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T18:20:20.000Z","msg":"9估<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IAMGkUZulvw\" data-s